{
  "stem": "10698.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and to every entrance to the building, somebody stood there so people couldn't run away, and they took all the people from the street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was either Jewish policeman-- at that time, we had Jewish policeman-- or [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Nazis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm so careful not to say Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you couldn't run in, and they grabbed all the people from the street on the-- on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, lo and behold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We look around, and there's one place-- one-- one entrance to the building that nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We ran in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We ran into the super-- at that time, was a Jewish super.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, will you hide us?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, I cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But go upstairs-- all the way upstairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And from the attic, there is a thing to-- an opening to go out on the roof.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Can you imagine my mom, being in her late '50s at that time, to go up four flights, go up into the attic of the building and climb out on the roof and hiding behind the chimney?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the God's truth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, my family at that time-- my father was still, my sister, my brother-in-law-- they all thought that we are goners.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they heard about that block and they knew that we had to cross that street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the super eventually came up to tell us that they are gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came home, and we quickly, quickly-- we made a package of certain things, foods and things, and brought it to that super.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the kind of people my parents were, always thanking people.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
